2000-10-30  Jesper Skov  <jskov@redhat.com>

	* cdl/synch.cdl: Replaced CYGINT_KERNEL_SCHEDULER_CAN_YIELD with
	CYGINT_KERNEL_SCHEDULER_UNIQUE_PRIORITIES.
