	Rename CYG_EXCEPTION_* -> CYGNUM_HAL_EXCEPTION_* in line
	with HAL changes
	Allow for CYGNUM_HAL_EXCEPTION_MIN != 0
	Rename deliver_exception() -> cyg_hal_deliver_exception()
	Add more tracing, and fix some existing
	QA improvements

